#: Anomaly id 103078 | Guide id 82
msgid "If Pirates/Nagas are in, use [[Brann Bronzebeard||96786]]/[[Sky Admiral Rogers||122516]], [[Captain Sanders||97539]], and [[Sea Witch Zar'jira||103069]] to go infinite and pick the highest scaling line. ADVANCED: After infinite, some very high cap builds include making a big Futurefin and scale more futurefins, or making a big Kodo and duplicate it with [[Stitched Salvager||119666]]"
msgstr "如果海盗/纳迦存在，使用 [[布莱恩·铜须||96786]]/[[空军上将罗杰斯||122516]]、[[杉德尔船长||97539]] 和 [[海巫扎尔吉拉||103069]] 无限刷钱并选择最高等级的成长线。进阶：无限经济后，有一些非常高上限的构筑，包括制作一个巨大的未来鱼人来成长和传播，或者制作一个巨大的科多兽，并用 [[缝合回收者||119666]] 复制它"

#: Anomaly id 131414 | Guide id 113
msgid "The most common strat is to flag a battlecry such as [[Hunting Tiger Shark||128168]] and cycle it a lot with [[Brann Bronzebeard||96786]]. The other strat is to flag a [[Tortallan Blue Shell]] and go infinite that turn. Artanis specifically could copy a lot of immortals, and Jim Raynor can make multiple battlecruisers."
msgstr ""

#: Anomaly id 128772 | Guide id 111
msgid "Immortal, Chameleon, and Mythrax tend to be insane ending units that get added to the pool."
msgstr "不朽者，变色龙和米斯拉克斯往往都是卡池中的疯狂的决赛随从。"

#: Anomaly id 131637 | Guide id 117
msgid "The best 4 drops to pick are the ones that generate value every turn such as [[Bigwig Bandit||122179]]."
msgstr "最佳的4级随从是每回合都能产生价值的，例如 [[顶尖大盗||122179]]。"

#: Anomaly id 119044 | Guide id 58
msgid "ALWAYS go 3 on 3! Then you can golden a 3 drop on turn 4 and triple into a 4 drop. Use your 3rd arrow on something that wins you the game like golden Brann or Titus."
msgstr "始终第3回合升到3级！这样你就能在第4回合获得金色3级随从，然后获得一个4级三连奖励。将第3支箭用在能让你赢得游戏的地方，比如金铜须或瑞文戴尔。"

#: Anomaly id 102046 | Guide id 41
msgid "If you have buffs or spellcraft in your hand, use the buffs on the shop and then buy the minion with double header to duplicate the buffs."
msgstr "如果手中有buff或塑造法术，就对酒馆里的随从使用buff，然后使用“双头之战”购买随从来复制 buff。"

#: Anomaly id 119094 | Guide id 22
msgid "For your second hero power, generally the lower armor the hero is, the better option it is. For example, Snake eyes is one of the best second hero powers to pick because it's a 6 armor hero paired alongside the armor of your first hero. Patchwerk technically counts as a 0 armor hero so it's one of the best second hero powers."
msgstr "对于你的第二个英雄技能，一般来说护甲越低的英雄越好。例如，“蛇眼 ”是最好的第二个英雄技能之一，因为她是一个6护甲的英雄，与第一个英雄的护甲组合在一起。从技术上讲，帕奇维克算是一个0护甲的英雄，所以它是最好的第二个英雄技能之一。"

#: Anomaly id 107226 | Guide id 21
msgid "If there's an OP card that synergizes with another hero in the lobby very well (eg. battlecry with Shudderwock/Brann), then don't give it to them. On the contrary, pick cards that are OP for your hero/comp but not other people's."
msgstr "如果有一张超模卡牌能与大厅中的其他英雄产生很好的协同效应（例如战吼与沙德沃克/布莱恩·铜须的协同效应），那就不要给他们。相反，选择那些对你的英雄/流派来说超模但对其他人来说不算超模的卡牌。"

#: Anomaly id 102075 | Guide id 25
msgid "Useless triples are less valuable because they don't give you a triple reward. If you don't plan on keeping a card, don't triple it."
msgstr "无用的三连没那么重要，因为它们不会给你三连奖励。如果你不打算留下这个随从，请不要三连。"

#: Anomaly id 131413 | Guide id 114
msgid "Trinkets that give a card start of your turn will give you a card when you pick it and a card the next turn, so value these trinkets highly."
msgstr ""

#: Anomaly id 103541 | Guide id 70
msgid "Early value generating buddies are premium. Buddies are usually just much better cards than the regular minion pool. ADVANCED: A common scaling line in Elemental lobbies are to go infinite with Brann and then scaling using ballers. You should have golden Reliquary Attendants (Taethalan Buddy) to copy multiple baller spells every turn and also Jandice Buddy."
msgstr "早期产生价值的伙伴是优质的。伙伴通常是比普通的随从池中的卡牌好得多。进阶：在元素局中，一个常见的扩展路线是与布莱恩·铜须达成无限经济，然后使用投球手进行成长。你应该拥有金色的遗物学会侍从（泰瑟兰·血望者的伙伴），每回合复制多个投球手法术，并且还有詹迪斯的伙伴。"

#: Anomaly id 129427 | Guide id 109
msgid "The best T1 prizes to take are Codex, Gacha Gift. The best T2 prize to take is On The House. The best T3 prize is Mindflayer Goggles."
msgstr "最好的第1回合奖品是秘典，抽卡赠礼。 最好的第2回合奖品是免费酬宾。最好的第3回合奖品是夺心护目镜。"

#: Anomaly id 102085 | Guide id 43
msgid "Level very fast in this one. Most of the time you're going level 4 on turn 4, or at the very least tavern 4 by turn 5."
msgstr "快速升级酒馆。大多数情况下，你要在第4回合升到4级，或者至少在第5回合升到4级。"

#: Anomaly id 102459 | Guide id 84
msgid "Usually, you level to tavern 2 on turn 2, then tavern 3 on turn 4. The best T1 prizes to take are Codex, Gacha Gift. The best T2 prizes to take is On The House. The best T3 prizes is Mindflayer Goggles."
msgstr "通常情况下，在第2回合升到2级酒馆，然后在第4回合升到3级酒馆。等级1的最佳暗月奖品是“秘典”，“抽卡赠礼”。等级2的最佳暗月奖品是 “免费酬宾”。等级3的最佳暗月奖品是“夺心护目镜”"

#: Anomaly id 102084 | Guide id 45
msgid "Morchie and Murozond are amazing because you can golden your timewarp. Zerek can golden something then copy it."
msgstr ""

